data.description: Welcome to your elegant and modern retreat. This home features a main floor primary suite, complemented by an oversized yard that backs up to a tranquil green space. The open concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for hosting gatherings with loved ones. The kitchen boasts sleek smart appliances and a 5 burner gas cooktop, ensuring you have everything you need to prepare culinary delights. Explore the nearby walking trails, immersing yourself in nature's beauty at your doorstep. And with remote-controlled window shades, you can effortlessly create the ideal atmosphere with just a touch. Embrace an optional low-maintenance lifestyle and find your peace in this beautiful sanctuary.
